episodes.title: Covert Central: Uncovering Child Abduction, Cults, and a High-Stakes Cross-State Pursuit
episodes.description: Join Bryan and Justin, Miami private investigators, as they explore one of their most complex child abduction cases, involving a cult. In this video, they break down the investigation, sharing key details and the challenges they encountered along the way. Watch for an inside look at the case and the investigation process.,
